    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>心能特工</strong>》是一款快节奏团队战术射击游戏。游戏中，四支队伍将斗智斗勇，目的是争夺用来维持生命的能量。邀请好友，制定取胜策略，使用独特的英雄技能，自定义武器配装和磁力“通量”能力，该能力能让你以前所未有的方式在场景中移动。《心能特工》邀请你感受脉搏，力挽狂澜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/200522634c8cb44bae5bcab2cb5c2d14.poster.avif?t=1761548909\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/200522634c8cb44bae5bcab2cb5c2d14.webm?t=1761548909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/200522634c8cb44bae5bcab2cb5c2d14.mp4?t=1761548909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《<strong>心能特工</strong>》中，战局瞬息万变。你是否会冒着成为众矢之的的风险，去抢夺一台心能装置？你是专心削弱一支敌方队伍，还是静候时机，在关键时刻向领先的队伍发难？胜利的关键在于读懂战局的脉搏，随机应变，在策略上胜过对手并力挽狂澜。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/e6b753ea75cea6fe034dc36edc5310ce.poster.avif?t=1761548909\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/e6b753ea75cea6fe034dc36edc5310ce.webm?t=1761548909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/e6b753ea75cea6fe034dc36edc5310ce.mp4?t=1761548909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组队与规划</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对3支敌方队伍，每场比赛都是充斥着合作、欺骗与突然反转的动态博弈。与你的队伍磨合以解锁新的战术，或打对手个措手不及。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/e40494a89f89cf40c04e9fa8222a9946.poster.avif?t=1761548909\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/e40494a89f89cf40c04e9fa8222a9946.webm?t=1761548909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/e40494a89f89cf40c04e9fa8222a9946.mp4?t=1761548909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造你的配装</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用专长、模组和武器来自定义配装，打造属于你自己的独特游戏风格。无论你是个高机动性的决斗者、战场控制者还是在关键时刻打辅助的玩家，找到自己的独特角色和战术，让敌人疲于招架。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/cf973fd5be79451126effee59c26866f.poster.avif?t=1761548909\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/cf973fd5be79451126effee59c26866f.webm?t=1761548909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392980/extras/cf973fd5be79451126effee59c26866f.mp4?t=1761548909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>社区驱动式开发</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家反馈在《心能特工》的开发过程中占核心地位。加入我们的Steam游戏测试和Discord社区并说出你的想法、测试新版本并帮助我们塑造游戏的未来。关注本游戏并将其添加至愿望单以了解最新动态，并告诉我们如何将《心能特工》打造成你最喜欢的FPS。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好感受脉搏并力挽狂澜了吗？来《心能特工》中一展身手吧。</p>",
